EN: He bound the hands and feet of the kidnapper together.

ZH: 我用皮筋把书捆成一束。
EN: I bundled the books together with elastic bands.

ZH: 他将报纸卷成一卷捆在一起。
EN: He rolled up the newspapers and bundled them together.

ZH: 妈妈把萝卜捆在一起放进冰箱。
EN: Mom tied the radishes together and put them in the refrigerator.

ZH: 为了方便携带，他把棍棒捆了起来。
EN: In order to carry it conveniently, he tied the stick into a bundle.

